title: Megyn Knox — Babe of the Day
text:
Share on Twitter Model Mayhem 
Megyn is a 23-year-old model and actress from LA who says she brings her ‘A-game’ to every shoot. 
If you’re looking for a ditzy, stuck-up, fashionably-late gal (is anyone ever looking for one of those, specifically?) Megyn says she’s not your gal. Megyn is a military veteran who toured for two years before becoming an agency model, so she knows the value of time. 
A former art student, Megyn loves looking at nude work, but only shoots “implied nude,” for career reasons. The reason probably being that we would all have heart attacks, and that’s bad for business. 
Check out her website to see more of her current work , and follow her on Instagram @gemmagypsy. 5’9″ | 140 lbs. | 32C-29-38
